B) Application Deployment  
C) Metric Collection  
D) Automated Alarms  
**Answer:** B  

2Ô∏è‚É£ **Which AWS service helps you track API activity, unlike CloudWatch?**  
A) AWS CloudTrail  
B) AWS Lambda  
C) AWS EC2  
D) AWS S3  
**Answer:** A  

3Ô∏è‚É£ **How do you create a custom metric in CloudWatch?**  
A) Through EC2 Dashboard  
B) Using AWS CLI or SDKs  
C) Only via AWS Management Console  
D) None of the above  
**Answer:** B  

4Ô∏è‚É£ **What is the default retention period for CloudWatch Logs?**  
A) 7 days  
B) 30 days  
C) Infinite unless specified  
D) 1 year  
**Answer:** C  

5Ô∏è‚É£ **Which service can trigger CloudWatch Alarms for automated responses?**  
A) AWS SNS  
B) AWS EC2  
C) AWS S3  
D) AWS Route 53  
**Answer:** A  

